            <!-- Breakthrough 1: Single-File Interactive Format -->
            <div class="info-card" style="margin-bottom: 30px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1) 0%, rgba(118, 75, 162, 0.1) 100%); border-left: 5px solid #667eea;">
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 15px;">
                    <h3 style="color: #667eea; margin: 0; flex: 1;">1. Single-File Interactive Image Format</h3>
                    <span style="background: #667eea; color: white; padding: 5px 12px; border-radius: 15px; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: bold;">‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê GENUINE BREAKTHROUGH</span>
                </div>
                <p style="color: #666; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 15px;">
                    <strong>What it is:</strong> A novel binary file format that combines image + metadata + interactivity + data layers in ONE self-contained file.
                </p>
                <p style="color: #666; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 15px;">
                    <strong>Why it's a breakthrough:</strong> No existing format combines image + interactivity + metadata in a single offline-capable file. 
                    Works 100% offline, universal compatibility (browser/desktop/HTML/PDF/PPTX), non-destructive (original pixels preserved).
                </p>
                <div style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.05); padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 15px;">
